<p><strong>More in depth</strong></p>
<div id="id-5"><img class="tw-inline" loading="lazy" src='/assets/images/2023/03/Bookstore-Container_Context_diagram_for_Bookstore_System.svg'   alt="c4 container diagram"  ></div>
